abrasives, electronics, and solar energy industries. In addition, the company offers various value added specialty fluoro intermediates consist of boron trifluoride gas and related adducts for pharmaceutical industry, as well as crop protection, hydrocarbon, and fragrance applications; and contract development and contract manufacturing services, such as basic research, library syntheses, process development, scale up, and small and batch manufacturing for custom chemical syntheses of fluorinated compounds in the pharmaceuticals, agro chemicals, and specialty chemicals industries. Navin Fluorine International Limited was founded in 1967 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}